name: skymansionx/Typing-Speed-Game
description: ⌨️ Typing Test Utility: A game designed to measure typing speed (WPM) and accuracy. ✍️ Utilizes text parsing and timing functions. Essential for coders! 💻

name: skymansionx/Media-Encoder-Tool
description: 🎞️ Media-Encoder-Tool: A web-based Video Converter utility that processes media files using browser APIs or a backend service. Handles various formats and resolutions. 🎥

name: skymansionx/Color-Matching-Game
description: 🟥 Color Matching Game: A game that tests visual memory. 🎨 Matches complex colors or patterns under time pressure. Focuses on psychological testing metrics. 🧠 ⏱️

name: skymansionx/Arcade-Bouncer-Game
description: 🏀 Arcade Bouncer Game: A recreation of Breakout featuring complex ball trajectory physics. 🎯 Excellent for mastering game loops and advanced level design. 💥

name: skymansionx/Escape-the-Room
description: 🚪 Escape the Room: A mystery puzzle game where users must find and combine clues. 💡 Solves complex problems to exit the virtual room. Focuses on environment design. 🔍 🧩

name: skymansionx/Code-Formatter-Plugin
description: ✨ Code Formatter Plugin: A plugin for a code editor (like VS Code) that automatically formats code according to a defined style guide. 🧹 Improves code consistency and readability. ✍️

name: skymansionx/Particle-System-Simulator
description: 🎆 Particle System Simulator: A particle effects tool designed to create and visualize various particle effects. ✨ Tweaks fire, smoke, and sparks using physics parameters. Focuses on rendering performance. ⚙️ 💻

name: skymansionx/Sudoku-Game
description: 🔢 Sudoku Game: A browser puzzle game implemented directly in the browser. 💡 Complete with puzzle generation and validation logic. Great for practicing recursion. 🧠 🧩

name: skymansionx/Racing-Championship-Sim
description: 🏁 Racing-Championship-Sim: A 3D Racing Game focusing on simple car controls and basic track geometry for a fun arcade experience. Great for physics simulation. 🏁

name: skymansionx/Space-Invaders-Reimagined
description: 👾 Arcade Revival Project: Modern reimagining of Space Invaders. 🚀 Features dynamic alien formations and challenging boss waves. Great for game dev practice! 🌌

name: skymansionx/VR-World-Builder
description: 🕶️ VR-World-Builder: A basic template for creating a simple Virtual Reality (VR) scene. 🌍 A great starting point for Oculus or WebVR development. 🕹️
